title: Help!
author: WickNilson
pages:
#- I leave this here message incase I dont return. On Thurdsday the 4th of April 2013, Balthazar19 attacked this keep with mallice and intent to steal. I steeled myself and bravely fought off the attack cursing him to damnation. Allthough I failed to pearl 
#- him and he is still at large. I now set off to capture and kill this son of a bitch. Burn him the firey hell that is the neether and then banish him to the end for the rest of his motherfucking days.

If you are reading this, then I have failed.
#- I am either killed or trapped in the end, hoping for relase. 

If you have found this, find Balthazar, kill him, Free me and you will be greatly rewarded with riches and land.

Wicknilson. Barron of Saltrock Hold.
#- 